OL,3,CIslanders learn stories behind
OL,4,CJersey's classroom in series of new
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FFor the first time, residents in
OL,8,FJersey can discover the history of the
OL,9,Fisland's schools, their ancestors and
OL,10,Fthe island's quirky school stories.
OL,12,FIt comes as Jersey Heritage is hosting
OL,13,Fits 'What's Your School Story'' series
OL,14,Fwhere once a month residents have a
OL,15,Fchance to learn about the teachers and
OL,16,Fpupils who sat in classrooms in years
OL,17,Fgone by.
