OL,7,FLinda Romeril, Head of Archives and
OL,8,FCollections at Jersey Heritage
OL,9,Fhighlights some of the island's
OL,10,Finteresting stories, such as
OL,11,Fprioritising the Jersey cow, she says:
OL,12,F"We have a great quote from when they
OL,13,Fwere talking about compulsory
OL,14,Feducation and one of the states
OL,15,Fmembers from the time was accusing
OL,16,Fothers of putting cows before
OL,17,Fchildren, he basically said, "We look
OL,18,Fafter our cows, we are very proud of
OL,19,Fcows but our children, well we don't
OL,20,Fmind if they are uneducated and if
OL,21,Fthey go off into the world without the
OL,22,Flearning that they need", so that is a
OL,23,Ffantastic quote and is really
OL,24,Finteresting to see how attitudes have
OL,25,Fchanged over the years."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
