OL,7,FLinda also says she hopes it
OL,8,Freconnects islanders to previous
OL,9,Fgenerations, she says: "Primary
OL,10,Fschools are such an important part of
OL,11,Four lives and we do really build up
OL,12,Fcommunities in those areas,
OL,13,Fparticularly with some of the
OL,14,Ftraditional parish schools where you
OL,15,Fsee generations of families going to
OL,16,Fthe same school.
