OL,7,FShe adds: "Education wasn't compulsory
OL,8,Funtil the late 19th Century and what's
OL,9,Finteresting is we often see in our
OL,10,Fearly log books, which are books from
OL,11,Fheadmasters, that particularly in
OL,12,Fthose country parishes, lots of
OL,13,Fchildren off of school to take part in
OL,14,Fthe potato picking, to the point where
OL,15,Fschools actually just have a break."
